LAGOS – The Redeemed Christian Church of God (RCCG), Comforters Assembly, Lagos Province 38 has concluded plans to unveil the much talked about new parish called “Tabernacle of Praise”. The inauguration is expected to take place on the 24th of January 2021, at Ijegun Road, Alimosho Local Government Area of Lagos. The cleric in charge of RCCG Comforters Assembly, Pastor Muyiwa Matilukuro, in a statement made available to DAILY INDEPENDENT said the initiative to establish a new parish was based on the 2nd mission of the church that has to do with the soul winning and for millions of people to make heaven.